Re: {!LeasePayment__c.Account__c} | Lease # {!LeasePayment__c.Lease__c} | Lease Date: {!LeasePayment__c.Date_Countersigned__c}
{!TODAY()}
Dear Lender:
SunPower Corporation (“SunPower”) agrees to comply with Fannie Mae’s “Requirements for Properties with a Solar Panels that are not Owned by the Borrower” (“Requirements”) provided in its Selling Guide Fannie Mae Single Family.
SunPower has recently been notified that the property located at {!LeasePayment__c.Site_Street__c}, {!LeasePayment__c.Site_City__c}, {!LeasePayment__c.Site_State_Prov__c} {!LeasePayment__c.Site_Zip_PostCode__c} is in the process of being refinanced or sold.
In the event the property listed above is foreclosed upon, SunPower agrees to comply with the Requirements.
Should you have any questions or concerns regarding what is contained in this acknowledgment, please do not hesitate to contact us at 800-321-1770, or send an email to homesale@sunpower.com (for home sale related inquiries) and refinance@sunpower.com (for refinancing and reverse mortgage inquiries) Monday through Friday between 9:00 a.m. and 5:00 p.m. (PST).
Attachments:
General Liability Insurance Certificate
Acknowledgment Agreement for Solar Energy
